<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF4C6AF3FA8595BC18DEBF34" bold="true" box="[1401,1758,997,1030]" pageId="183" pageNumber="945">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Known specimens of the Diminutive 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF4C6AF3F8ED9254196BBF1C" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[1809,1899,1037,1070]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="183" pageNumber="945" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
came from highly fragmented habitat, and nearby protected areas might not be effective forits long-term survival.
</paragraph>
